items.name: SHELLY
items.description: Shelly's spread-fire shotgun blasts the other team with buckshot. Her Super destroys cover and keeps her opponents at a distance!

items.name: COLT
items.description: Colt fires an accurate burst of bullets from his dual revolvers. His Super shreds cover and extends the bullet barrage!

items.name: BULL
items.description: Bull deals massive damage up close with his shotgun. For his Super move, he charges through barriers and knocks back enemies!

items.name: BROCK
items.description: Brock fires a long-range, explosive rocket at enemies. His Super is a ballistic rocket barrage that destroys cover!

items.name: RICO
items.description: Rico fires a burst of bullets that bounce off walls. His Super burst is a long barrage of bouncy bullets that pierce targets!

items.name: SPIKE
items.description: Spike throws cactus grenades that send needles flying, and a show-stopping Super: a field of cactus spines that slows down and damages enemies!

items.name: BARLEY
items.description: Barley attacks by lobbing bottles at enemies, doing splash damage. His Super is a huge barrage of burning bottles!

items.name: JESSIE
items.description: Jessie's Shock Rifle shoots energy orbs that bounce between enemies. Her Super deploys a cute but deadly gun turret!

items.name: NITA
items.description: Nita strikes her enemies with a thunderous shockwave. Her Super summons a massive bear to fight by her side!

items.name: DYNAMIKE
items.description: Dynamike lobs two explosive sticks of dynamite. His Super attack is a whole barrel full of dynamite that blows up cover!

items.name: EL PRIMO
items.description: El Primo throws a flurry of punches at his enemies. His Super is a leaping elbow drop that deals damage to all caught underneath!

items.name: MORTIS
items.description: Mortis dashes forward with each swing of his shovel. As his Super attack, he sends a cloud of bats to damage enemies and heal himself!

items.name: CROW
items.description: Crow fires a trio of poisoned daggers. As a Super move he leaps, firing daggers both on jump and on landing!

items.name: POCO
items.description: Poco fires damaging sound waves at enemies. His Super can heal both Poco himself and his teammates!

items.name: BO
items.description: Bo fires three explosive arrows toward his targets. His Super ability places a trio of hidden, explosive mines on the ground!

items.name: PIPER
items.description: Piper's sniper shots do more damage the farther they travel. Her Super drops grenades at her feet, while Piper herself leaps away!

items.name: PAM
items.description: Pam shoots from the hip, peppering targets with shrapnel. Her Super is a healing turret that restores her and teammates' health!

items.name: TARA
items.description: Tara's triple tarot card attack pierces through enemies. Her Super is a black hole that sucks in all nearby enemies, causing damage!

items.name: DARRYL
items.description: Darryl has a powerful double-shotgun attack. His Super move is a reckless roll inside his bouncy barrel!

items.name: PENNY
items.description: Penny shoots bags of coins, damaging the target and anyone standing behind. Her Super is a mortar-style cannon turret!

items.name: FRANK
items.description: Frank swings his hammer at enemies, sending a shockwave. His Super is an especially powerful blow that stuns enemies!

items.name: GENE
items.description: Gene uses his magic lamp to shoot a splitting projectile. His super is a magical hand that grabs and pulls enemies close!

items.name: TICK
items.description: Tick is a metal ball of barely controlled excitement and energy - explosive energy! He throws mines, and his Super makes his head detach, seek a target and explode.

items.name: LEON
items.description: Leon shoots a quick salvo of blades at his target. His Super trick is a smoke bomb that makes him invisible for a little while!

items.name: ROSA
items.description: This boxing botanist will plant her feet and go toe to toe! Her Super gives her tough, vegan protective gear.

items.name: CARL
items.description: Carl throws his Pickaxe like a boomerang. His Super is a crazy cart spin that clobbers anyone around him.

items.name: BIBI
items.description: Batter up! Bibi's got a sweet swing that can knock back enemies when her Home Run bar is charged. Her Super is a bouncing ball of gum that deals damage.

items.name: 8-BIT
items.description: 8-Bit lumbers along like an arcade cabinet on legs. He shoots Blaster Beams and his Super boosts friendlies' damage!

items.name: SANDY
items.description: Sandy is a sleep-deprived Brawler with powerful control over sand: casting sharp pebbles at enemies, and summoning a sandstorm to hide teammates.

items.name: BEA
items.description: Bea loves bugs and hugs. She shoots her mechanical drones at range, and her Super sends forth an angry army of swarming bees!

items.name: EMZ
items.description: Emz attacks with blasts of hair spray that deal damage over time, and slows down opponents with her Super.

items.name: MR. P
items.description: Mr. P is a disgruntled luggage handler who angrily hurls suitcases at opponents. His Super calls robo-porters to help him.

items.name: MAX
items.description: Max goes fast! Her attack is a fast-firing blaster. Her Super speeds up her and allies!

items.name: JACKY
items.description: Jacky works her Jackhammer to shake up the ground and nearby enemies. Her Super pulls in nearby foes, leaving them in the dust!

items.name: SPROUT
items.description: Sprout was built to plant life, launching bouncy Seed Bombs with reckless love. Its Super creates a blant-based obstacle!
